.sp
As of MySQL 5\&.5\&.3,
\fBmysqlhotcopy\fR
uses
FLUSH TABLES \fItbl_list\fR WITH READ LOCK
to flush and lock tables\&. Use the
\fB\-\-old_server\fR
option if the server is older than 5\&.5\&.3, which is when that statement was introduced\&. This option was added in MySQL 5\&.5\&.3\&.
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
